{
  "stem": "5613.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you wouldn't believe how much you accumulate, even in a prisoner of war camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There's so much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everybody-- I mean, we left most of it behind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But everybody was loaded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And by the way, this was the coldest winter of the war, '45.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was the worst.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The snow-- the ice and snow was very-- 20 inches.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And next morning, we had to schlep to the station and on the ice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we had to wait for-- I don't know how many-- two or three hours-- before a train come-- came.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the train was a cattle train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This was really a cattle train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they-- we went in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were traveling till next morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We went-- we left Kreuzburg at about 1 or 2 o'clock in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we arrived at 6:00 next morning in Breslau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's a big town, which is also Poland now, I believe, Breslau.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there, they took us to a school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I remember that in this train, I was sick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I had diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was no room to-- to stand, yes, but I was sitting in the corner with my legs folded up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I couldn't move, all the way to Breslau till next morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And when we came to the school I was sick as a dog.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the next day, I felt a bit better.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we stayed there from Friday night-- Saturday morning till Monday morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "On Monday morning, they put us on another train.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we travelled for 10 days to Austria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, this was a passenger-- a regular passenger train, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had an experience on this trip as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
